column2: SELECT m.id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, o.run, o.rerun, o.field, o.obj, n.objid, o.mode, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.SPLUS_marcus_cross from MyDB.SPLUS_DR1_objs_from_marcus_class_ra_dec_pairs AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
